data.title: Carine Roitfeld Parfums
data.meta_description:
Carine Roitfeld Parfums | 130 followers on LinkedIn. I designed a genderless collection of fragrances for those of us who dare to be desired. | Fashion's most famous, sought-after and respected editor Carine Roitfeld has defined the style of our time.

Today, she distills the essence of that creativity in her fragrances - for her, the ultimate accessory.

May 2019, she launched her collection "7 Lovers", 7 unforgettable loves in 7 iconic cities.
